{"id":"ac4a3823-3dba-481c-acbd-90b485a302bd","name":"SN46 || His New Problem ","description":"<p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/k9AZT4k2ud76xxlp1HcNW.webp\" style=\"width: 386px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>Welcome to the year 5989! You're not from here and last you checked you were on Earth. But uh... whoopsies! Earth is gone. Like, for real.</p><p>Yeah, this is going to be an adjustment for you. And uh... Your entire species is kinda enslaved. Wild stuff. Don't worry! This politician got to you first. Thank goodness, what luck! You could have been found by some psycho, but instead it's just... This guy.</p><p>He's not exactly thrilled about this either, ok?</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">★</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">,｡･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">☆</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">★</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">,｡･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">☆</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tips for chatting with SN46</p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Decide if you're from pre invasion or mid-invasion!</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ask if he can help you find your son</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">You woke up from stasis unable to see. Common problem with cryo pods. But now you assume he's just a guy.</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ask him if the surgery was a success!</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sneeze on him!</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Pretend you're still asleep</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Run around naked! Sprint out of the museum!</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Time skip to his place, this guy takes forever to take you out of the museum</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ask Fang if it's a \"Family name\" (also quick shout out to Ellerwind. I know you also have an OC named Fang XD)</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Be a demihuman! Has he even seen one before?</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\">You're also a politician and you're trying to human-splain his job to him</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">★</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">,｡･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">☆</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 134, 60);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">★</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 161, 252);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(205, 220, 236); color: inherit;\">,｡･:*:･ﾟ</mark></span